'''左翼团结'''（{{lang-en|Left Unity}}）是[[英国|英国]]的一个[[左翼|左翼]]政党，成立于2013年11月30日。在此之前，著名电影导演[[肯·洛奇|肯·洛奇]]呼吁成立一个替代[[工党_(英国)|工党]]的左翼政党，他批评工党未能反对[[紧缩|紧缩]]政策并转向了[[新自由主义|新自由主义]]。<ref name=LoachGuardian>{{cite web|title=The Labour party has failed us. We need a new party of the left|url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2013/mar/25/labour-party-left|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2013-12-04|date=25 March 2013|archive-date=2013-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206152931/http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2013/mar/25/labour-party-left|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Seymour|first1=Richard|title=Left Unity: A Report From The Founding Conference|url=http://www.newleftproject.org/index.php/site/article_comments/left_unity_a_report_from_the_founding_conference|website=newleftproject.org|publisher=New Left Project|accessdate=2015-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402122037/http://www.newleftproject.org/index.php/site/article_comments/left_unity_a_report_from_the_founding_conference|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rpmSDc1nBvE |title=RT News reports on Left Unity's founding conference |accessdate=2013-12-04 |archive-date=2020-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015141055/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rpmSDc1nBvE |dead-url=no }}</ref>超过10000人在洛奇的最初倡议上署名。<ref name=LoachHuffpost>{{cite web|title=Ken Loach Discusses His Hopes for Left Unity|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/salman-shaheen/ken-loach-left-unity_b_4302871.html|publisher=The Huffington Post UK|accessdate=2013-12-04|date=20 November 2013|archive-date=2018-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031005247/https://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/salman-shaheen/ken-loach-left-unity_b_4302871.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年，该党拥有2000名成员<ref>{{cite web|title=New party Left Unity to hold first annual conference|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-29799731|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|accessdate=2015-03-06|date=11 November 2014|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314170920/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-29799731|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在全英国组建了70个支部。<ref name="LU conference">{{cite web|title=Left Unity conference – some important steps forward and challenges still ahead|url=http://socialistresistance.org/6911/left-unity-conference-some-important-steps-forward-and-challenges-still-ahead|publisher=Socialist Resistance|accessdate=2015-03-07|archive-date=2016-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160904221613/http://socialistresistance.org/6911/left-unity-conference-some-important-steps-forward-and-challenges-still-ahead|dead-url=no}}</ref>该党是[[欧洲左翼党|欧洲左翼党]]的成员党。

==组织==
该党的成立得到了以下政党和组织的支持，它们鼓励自己的成员加入左翼团结：
*[[争取工人自由联盟|争取工人自由联盟]]
*[[大不列颠共产党_(临时中央委员会)|大不列颠共产党 (临时中央委员会)]]
*[[国际社会主义网络|国际社会主义网络]]
*[[社会主义抵抗|社会主义抵抗]]
*[[工人力量|工人力量]]

工党和[[英格兰和威尔士绿党|英格兰和威尔士绿党]]的一些成员也加入了该党。

2014年2月8日，大不列颠共产党 (临时中央委员会)在该党内部建立了一个名为“左翼团结共产主义纲领”的长期性派别。

